  "texts": [
    "In the next section, for any rational r > 1,",
    "• we construct a connected motif G fulfilling the key condition (14);",
    "• we prove that when q ≍ n -1/r and (2) hold, we can recover the communities in the SBM with an algorithm based on P G.",
    "The family of motifs G is based on the blow-up of a cycle.",
    "Writing r = γ + a with γ an integer larger than 1 and a a rational in (0, 1), the motif is constructed by considering a γ-blow-up of a cycle of length κ, that we link evenly to i and j with aκγ edges -called fasteners in the following."
  ],
